Package: lctmr
Title: Latent Class Trajectory Modeling for Growth Data
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R:
    person("Evan", "Liu", , "naoliu@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Performs Latent Class Trajectory Modeling (LCTM) to identify
    hidden subgroups of individuals with distinct growth patterns over time.
    Provides a layered API with high-level automation, mid-level step-by-step
    functions, and low-level utilities for advanced users. Implements model
    adequacy checks including APPA, OCC, and relative entropy metrics.
